/android/app/release

# #315 — gen-l10n output. Machine-generated from lib/l10n/*.arb at `flutter pub
# get` (the `generate: true` flag in pubspec.yaml), so CI's pub get → analyze →
# test order always produces it before anything reads it. Committing it would
# mean review noise on every copy change and a tree that can silently disagree
# with the ARBs it came from. The ARBs ARE tracked — they are the source.
lib/l10n/gen/
